{"id":232901404,"title":"#分享 忘記資料放在哪個雲端硬碟？FYI 讓你一鍵搜尋找到檔案！","content":"臨時要找一個很久沒碰的檔案，卻早就忘記放在哪個雲端硬碟上嗎？試試看 FYI 這個瀏覽器擴充套件吧，它能夠讓你一次搜尋多個雲端硬碟。\n\n不知道大家有沒有遇過這樣的情況，同時間跟不同團隊的人合作，有些文件可能存在個人雲端硬碟、有些可能放在共用雲端裡， 但一次整合到 FYI 上就不用開啟許多分頁，我知道這項產品後真的節省很多找資料的時間，而且 FYI 不但免費還支援中文搜尋，所以想推薦給有需要的人！\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/7rlAd2d.png\n（左欄 Activity Feed 讓你知道今天、昨天有誰編輯過檔案、在什麼時候編輯了什麼檔案等。圖：FYI）\n\nhttp://i.imgur.com/IMOc5HD.png\n（右欄則列出你的聯繫人，點選人像可以看到你跟對方共享的所有檔案。圖：FYI）\n\n文章：\nhttps://medium.com/starrocket/fyi-a-browser-extension-helps-you-find-the-files-from-every-cloud-drive-95c27f985ec9","excerpt":"臨時要找一個很久沒碰的檔案，卻早就忘記放在哪個雲端硬碟上嗎？試試看 FYI 這個瀏覽器擴充套件吧，它能夠讓你一次搜尋多個雲端硬碟。不知道大家有沒有遇過這樣的情況，同時間跟不同團隊的人合作，有些文件可能","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"577f29b9-ef96-4e05-9e79-55e2a7d6e3db","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-16T10:26:25.206Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-16T10:30:00.867Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":3,"tags":[],"topics":["軟體","雲端","電腦","分享"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"App","forumAlias":"app","school":"鄧天天","department":"kfclover","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":3}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/7rlAd2d.png"},{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/IMOc5HD.png"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"7c2937fe-d14e-4aac-a8f3-a3df947798be","url":"https://i.imgur.com/7rlAd2dl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/7rlAd2dl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/7rlAd2dl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-16T10:30:00.867Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-16T10:30:00.867Z"},{"id":"7c2937fe-d14e-4aac-a8f3-a3df947798be","url":"http://i.imgur.com/7rlAd2d.png","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/7rlAd2d","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/7rlAd2dl.j